attributes.name: VK_MAX_MEMORY_HEAPS
attributes.comment: The maximum number of unique memory heaps, each of which supporting 1 or more memory types

attributes.name: VK_IMAGE_LAYOUT_UNDEFINED
attributes.comment: Implicit layout an image is when its contents are undefined due to various reasons (e.g. right after creation)

attributes.name: VK_IMAGE_LAYOUT_GENERAL
attributes.comment: General layout when image can be used for any kind of access

attributes.name: VK_IMAGE_LAYOUT_COLOR_ATTACHMENT_OPTIMAL
attributes.comment: Optimal layout when image is only used for color attachment read/write

attributes.name: VK_IMAGE_LAYOUT_DEPTH_STENCIL_ATTACHMENT_OPTIMAL
attributes.comment: Optimal layout when image is only used for depth/stencil attachment read/write

attributes.comment: Optimal layout when image is used for read only depth/stencil attachment and shader access

attributes.name: VK_IMAGE_LAYOUT_SHADER_READ_ONLY_OPTIMAL
attributes.comment: Optimal layout when image is used for read only shader access

attributes.name: VK_IMAGE_LAYOUT_TRANSFER_SRC_OPTIMAL
attributes.comment: Optimal layout when image is used only as source of transfer operations

attributes.name: VK_IMAGE_LAYOUT_TRANSFER_DST_OPTIMAL
attributes.comment: Optimal layout when image is used only as destination of transfer operations

attributes.name: VK_IMAGE_LAYOUT_PREINITIALIZED
attributes.comment: Initial layout used when the data is populated by the CPU
